ium":false},{"id":"3209","title":"子陣列按位與值為 K 的數目","slug":"number-of-subarrays-with-and-value-of-k","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/number-of-subarrays-with-and-value-of-k/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false}],"children":[]},{"id":8,"title":"3.2 GCD LogTrick","isLeaf":true,"problems":[{"id":"2447","title":"最大公因數等於 K 的子陣列數目","slug":"number-of-subarrays-with-gcd-equal-to-k","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/number-of-subarrays-with-gcd-equal-to-k/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"2654","title":"使陣列所有元素變成 1 的最少操作次數","slug":"minimum-number-of-operations-to-make-all-array-elements-equal-to-1","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-number-of-operations-to-make-all-array-elements-equal-to-1/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"2941","title":"子陣列的最大 GCD-Sum","slug":"maximum-gcd-sum-of-a-subarray","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximum-gcd-sum-of-a-subarray/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":true},{"id":"3574","title":"最大子陣列 GCD 分數","slug":"maximize-subarray-gcd-score","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximize-subarray-gcd-score/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"3605","title":"陣列的最小穩定性因子","slug":"minimum-stability-factor-of-array","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-stability-factor-of-array/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false}],"children":[]}],"summary":"AND 的數越多，結果越小。\n\nOR 的數越多，結果越大。\n\n### AND/OR LogTrick\n\n[LogTrick 入門教程](/link/?target=https%3A%2F%2Fzhuanlan.zhihu.com%2Fp%2F1933215367158830792)，包含原地寫法，以及額外維護一個列表的寫法。\n\n如果你不熟悉原地去重演算法，可以看 [26\\. 刪除有序陣列中的重複項](https://leetcode.cn/problems/remove-duplicates-from-sorted-array/)，[我的題解](https://leetcode.cn/problems/remove-duplicates-from-sorted-array/solutions/2807162/gen-zhao-wo-guo-yi-bian-shi-li-2ni-jiu-m-rvyk/)。\n\n模板：\n\n```py\n# 對於每個右端點 i，計算所有子陣列的或值，列印這些或值的分佈範圍（子陣列左端點範圍）\n# 時間複雜度 O(nlogU)，其中 U = max(nums)\ndef logTrick(nums: List[int]) -> None:\n    or_left = []  # (子陣列或值，最小左端點)\n    for i, x in enumerate(nums):\n        # 計算以 i 為右端點的子陣列或值\n        for p in or_left:\n            p[0] |= x  # **根據題目修改**\n        # x 單獨一個數作為子陣列\n        or_left.append([x, i])\n\n        # 原地去重（相同或值只保留最左邊的）\n        idx = 1\n        for j in range(1, len(or_left)):\n            if or_left[j][0] != or_left[j - 1][0]:\n                or_left[idx] = or_left[j]\n                idx += 1\n        del or_left[idx:]\n\n        print(i, x)\n        for k, (or_val, left) in enumerate(or_left):\n            right = or_left[k + 1][1] - 1 if k < len(or_left) - 1 else i\n            # 對於左端點在 [left, right]，右端點為 i 的子陣列，OR 值都是 or_val\n            print(left, right, or_val)\n\nlogTrick([4, 2, 1, 5])\n```\n\n注：下面的部分題目，可以用**滑動視窗+堆疊**做到更優的 O(n) 時間複雜度，見 [原理講解（方法二）](https://leetcode.cn/problems/find-subarray-with-bitwise-or-closest-to-k/solutions/2798206/li-yong-and-de-xing-zhi-pythonjavacgo-by-gg4d/)。\n\n### GCD LogTrick\n\n*   [2447\\. 最大公因數等於 K 的子陣列數目](https://leetcode.cn/problems/number-of-subarrays-with-gcd-equal-to-k/) 非暴力做法\n*   [2654\\. 使陣列所有元素變成 1 的最少操作次數](https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-number-of-operations-to-make-all-array-elements-equal-to-1/) 非暴力做法\n*   [3605\\. 陣列的最小穩定性因子](https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-stability-factor-of-array/) 2410\n*   [3574\\. 最大子陣列 GCD 分數](https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximize-subarray-gcd-score/) 非暴力做法\n*   [2941\\. 子陣列的最大 GCD-Sum](https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximum-gcd-sum-of-a-subarray/)（會員題）"},{"id":9,"title":"4. 拆位 / 貢獻法","isLeaf":false,"problems":[{"id":"477","title":"漢明距離總和","slug":"total-hamming-distance","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/total-hamming-distance/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"1835","title":"所有數對按位與結果的異或和","slug":"find-xor-sum-of-all-pairs-bitwise-and","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/find-xor-sum-of-all-pairs-bitwise-and/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"1863","title":"找出所有子集的異或總和再求和","slug":"sum-of-all-subset-xor-totals","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/sum-of-all-su