en":[],"summary":"[講解](/link/?target=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2FBV1pm8vzAEXx%2F)\n\n模板（最大異或和）：\n\n```py\nclass XorBasis:\n    # n 為值域最大值 U 的二進位制長度，例如 U=1e9 時 n=30\n    def __init__(self, n: int):\n        self.b = [0] * n\n\n    def insert(self, x: int) -> None:\n        b = self.b\n        # 從高到低遍歷，保證計算 max_xor 的時候，參與 XOR 的基的最高位（或者說二進位制長度）是互不相同的\n        for i in range(len(b) - 1, -1, -1):\n            if x >> i:  # 由於大於 i 的位都被我們異或成了 0，所以 x >> i 的結果只能是 0 或 1\n                if b[i] == 0:  # x 和之前的基是線性無關的\n                    b[i] = x  # 新增一個基，最高位為 i\n                    return\n                x ^= b[i]  # 保證每個基的二進位制長度互不相同\n        # 正常迴圈結束，此時 x=0，說明一開始的 x 可以被已有基表出，不是一個線性無關基\n\n    def max_xor(self) -> int:\n        b = self.b\n        res = 0\n        # 從高到低貪心：越高的位，越必須是 1\n        # 由於每個位的基至多一個，所以每個位只需考慮異或一個基，若能變大，則異或之\n        for i in range(len(b) - 1, -1, -1):\n            if res ^ b[i] > res:  # 手寫 max 更快\n                res ^= b[i]\n        return res\n```"},{"id":14,"title":"8. 思維題","isLeaf":true,"problems":[{"id":"810","title":"黑板異或遊戲","slug":"chalkboard-xor-game","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/chalkboard-xor-game/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"1558","title":"得到目標陣列的最少函式呼叫次數","slug":"minimum-numbers-of-function-calls-to-make-target-array","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-numbers-of-function-calls-to-make-target-array/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"2509","title":"查詢樹中環的長度","slug":"cycle-length-queries-in-a-tree","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/cycle-length-queries-in-a-tree/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"2546","title":"執行逐位運算使字串相等","slug":"apply-bitwise-operations-to-make-strings-equal","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/apply-bitwise-operations-to-make-strings-equal/","solution":null,"score":null,"isPremium":false},{"id":"2568","title":"最小無法得到的或值","slug":"minimum-impossible-or","src":"https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-impossible-or/","soluti